        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "`ch` is the column the cursor is at in the current line,         `ln` is the current line number,         `ct` is the total line numbers in the file (count).",
          "target": "`ch` 是光标在当前行的列位置，         `ln` 是当前行号，         `ct` 是文件中的总行数（计数）。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "If `ct` is the first or last of the three values,         it will be removed when displaying a range.",
          "target": "如果 `ct` 是三个值中的第一个或最后一个，         在显示范围时它将被移除。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "For example, with the default value of '12' the status bar         could be set to a width of 60 if the contents width is 55.",
          "target": "例如，使用默认值 '12'，如果内容宽度为 55，         状态栏的宽度可以设置为 60。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "A cursor with just the head is around 70px.         A single selection with head and anchor plus totals is around 250px.         3 selections like the above with individual line counts is around 500px.",
          "target": "一个只有头部的光标大约 70px。         一个带有头部和锚点以及总计的单次选择大约 250px。         像上面那样带有单独行计数的 3 次选择大约 500px。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setName",
          "source": "Number of cursor positions that will display           in the status bar before switching to \"N cursors\".",
          "target": "在切换到“N 个光标”之前，状态栏中显示的光标位置数量。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setName",
          "source": "Display just the beginning,         just the end, or the full range of a selection.",
          "target": "仅显示选择的起始位置、         结束位置，或完整范围。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setName",
          "source": "Display the total number of characters selected.",
          "target": "显示选中的总字符数。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setName",
          "source": "Display the total number of lines selected.",
          "target": "显示选中的总行数。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setName",
          "source": "Pattern to display location information for each cursor.",
          "target": "用于显示每个光标位置信息的模式。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setName",
          "source": "Custom pattern for display",
          "target": "自定义显示模式"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setName",
          "source": "String to seperate multiple curor locations when         `# of Cursors` is greater than 1. Selecting `custom`         will let you type out your own",
          "target": "当 `光标数量` 大于 1 时，用于分隔多个光标位置的字符串。选择 `自定义`         将允许您输入自己的字符串。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setName",
          "source": "String will be padded by a space on each side.         Consecutive whitespace is squashed to 1 space (per HTML rules).         For example: '/' will be displayed as ' / '",
          "target": "字符串两侧将用空格填充。         连续的空白字符将被压缩为 1 个空格（根据 HTML 规则）。         例如：'/' 将显示为 ' / '"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setName",
          "source": "String to seperate the beginning and end of a selection           when `Selection Mode` is set to `Full Selection`.           Selecting `custom` will let you type out your own",
          "target": "当 `选择模式` 设置为 `完整选择` 时，用于分隔选择起始和结束位置的字符串。           选择 `自定义` 将允许您输入自己的字符串。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setName",
          "source": "String will NOT be padded by a space on each side.           Consecutive whitespace is squashed to 1 space (per HTML rules)           For example: '->' will be displayed as '2->3' and ' -> ' will           be displayed as '2 -> 3'",
          "target": "字符串两侧将不会用空格填充。           连续的空白字符将被压缩为 1 个空格（根据 HTML 规则）。           例如：'->' 将显示为 '2->3'，而 ' -> ' 将显示为 '2 -> 3'"
        },
